      "name": "Reading the Runes",
      "description": "When this character activates, you may guess a card (colour and number/Catastrophe) then flip an Arcane Card. If you guessed correctly, apply the following effect: Green X: Choose a friendly Norse model within 8\" to gain Protection (The first time this character would suffer Dmg, reduce that Dmg to {Null}), until end of turn. Pink X: Choose a model within 8\" to suffer X Magical Dmg. Blue X: Choose a model within 8\" to restore X+1 Wds. Catastrophe: All models within 2\" suffer 2 Magical Dmg.",
